data.description: Come see this beautifully remodeled ranch style home with a large shop . This home has been fully remodeled with a gourmet kitchen that features granite countertops, gas appliances, farm style sink, stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar designed for entertaining. The primary bedroom features a full bathroom with a full tile shower with a conventional as well as a rainshower head. With a large vanity and WIC with custom organizers. The indoor laundry room has granite counters, lots of storage and a stainless wash station. The 500 sq ft covered back patio (plumbed for a gas fire pit) opens into a fully fenced backyard, hot tub and custom metal gates. Both yards have new sprinkler systems that are controlled through an app on your phone along with the drip system in the flower beds. Since 2012 the house has been replumbed with PEX plumbing, all new drainage (to include the sewer main), insulation, updated windows, doors and electrical service that has a built in whole home surge protector. The roof was also replaced in 2020.The shop is set up for anything from a hobby mechanic, welder, machinist or someone who needs a safe space for all of their toys! It features its own half bath with custom vanity, 120 amps of 220v power, is fully insulated, has wood heat and is pre-wired for an exterior 220v air compressor and car lift and is even wired for surround sound! Just outside the shop you'll also find a covering that is perfect for a full winter's worth of firewood. Wired for an EV charger hookup.
